TASK: Build the top-level Moon Build page component that wires everything together.

CONTEXT:
- useBuildPayload(workflowId) hook provides: payload, loading, error, mutate
- presentBuild(payload, selectedNodeId, orbitRadius) returns MoonBuildViewModel
- moonBuildReducer manages all UI state
- MoonOrbitSurface renders the orbit
- MoonDockHost + MoonDockStepper + MoonReleaseTray render the interaction layer
- Shell passes workflowId via props (from URL params)

